Class Event

java.lang.Object
com.iunera.jsonldjava.schemaorg.metadatatypes.Thing
com.iunera.jsonldjava.schemaorg.metadatatypes.Event
Direct Known Subclasses:
BusinessEvent, ChildrensEvent, ComedyEvent, DanceEvent, DeliveryEvent, EducationEvent, ExhibitionEvent, Festival, FoodEvent, LiteraryEvent, MusicEvent, PublicationEvent, SaleEvent, ScreeningEvent, SocialEvent, SportsEvent, TheaterEvent, VisualArtsEvent
public class Event extends Thing
An event happening at a certain time and location, such as a concert, lecture, or festival. Ticketing information may be added via the offers property. Repeated events may be structured as separate Event objects.

    • previousStartDate

      public Date previousStartDate
      Used in conjunction with eventStatus for rescheduled or cancelled events. This property contains the previously scheduled start date. For rescheduled events, the startDate property should be used for the newly scheduled start date. In the (rare) case of an event that has been postponed and rescheduled multiple times, this field may be repeated.
